# --- IDE & System ---
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# --- Dependencies & Build Artifacts ---
# Recursive: Catches node_modules in ANY folder
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/bin/
**/tmp/
**/.next/
**/.mintlify/
**/.cache/

# --- Go Specific ---
# Exclude compiled binaries
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test

# --- Secrets ---
# Use a wildcard to catch .env, .env.local, .env.development, etc.
.env*
!.env.example

# --- Logs ---
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*


# --- Local databases / assets ---
**/GeoLite2-*.mmdb
